                                    (Nomination) or Refused.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex relative group">
                        <div
                            class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 flex flex-col items-center"
                        >
                            <div
                                class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-green-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold z-10 text-sm shadow-md ring-4 ring-white"
                            >
                                ‚úì
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pl-4 flex-grow">
                            <div
                                class="bg-green-50 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-green-200 shadow-sm"
                            >
                                <h3
                                    class="text-lg font-bold text-green-900 mb-1"
                                >
                                    Federal PR Application
                                </h3>
                                <p class="text-green-800 text-sm">
                                    Apply to IRCC for Permanent Residence. You
                                    are almost there!
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <hr class="my-12 border-slate-200" />

                <h2>Phase 1: SIRS Registration (The "Pool")</h2>
                <div
                    class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-400 p-6 rounded-r-xl my-6 not-prose"
                >
                    <p
                        class="font-bold text-amber-900 mb-1 text-sm uppercase tracking-wide"
                    >
                        Technical Warning
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-amber-800 text-sm font-medium">
                        Do not use a phone or tablet. The <a
                            href="https://www.pnpapplication.gov.bc.ca/"
                            rel="nofollow"
                            class="underline hover:text-amber-950"
                            >BC PNP Online portal</a
                        > is old and buggy on mobile. Use a desktop computer with
                        Chrome or Firefox.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 not-prose">
                    <div
                        class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider"
                        >
                            Screen 1
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg mb-2">
                            Current Status
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">
                            You will be asked: <em
                                >"Do you have valid status in Canada?"</em
                            >
                        </p>
                        <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2">
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
                                <strong>Visitor:</strong> Select if on Visitor Record.
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
                                <strong>Worker:</strong> Enter expiry date carefully.
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
                                <strong>Maintained Status:</strong> Use the specific
                                checkbox/implied date.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider"
                        >
                            Screen 2
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg mb-2">
                            Job Offer Details
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">
                            The most critical section. Errors here cause
                            rejections.
                        </p>
                        <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2">
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
                                <strong>Job Title:</strong> Must match offer letter
                                exactly.
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
                                <strong>NOC Code:</strong> Double-check TEER level
                                vs duties.
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
                                <strong>Wage:</strong> Hourly base wage only. No tips/bonuses.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-blue-100 mt-6 not-prose"
                >
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-900 text-lg mb-2">
                        Education & Language Screen
                    </h3>
                    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                        <div>
                            <span
                                class="block text-xs font-bold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1"
                                >Education</span
                            >
                            <p class="text-blue-800 text-sm">
                                Only list education you can prove with a diploma
                                AND an ECA (if foreign). Don't list pending
                                degrees.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span
                                class="block text-xs font-bold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1"
                                >Language</span
                            >
                            <p class="text-blue-800 text-sm">
                                Enter the PIN/Registration number from your
                                IELTS/CELPIP form. System verifies this
                                instantly.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
