                    <span class="text-3xl mr-4">üéâ</span>
                    <div>
                        <p class="font-bold text-green-900">
                            Congratulations! You received an Invitation to Apply
                            (ITA).
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-green-800 text-sm">
                            Now the real work begins. You have exactly <strong
                                >30 days</strong
                            > to submit.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 not-prose">
                    <div
                        class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm"
                    >
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg mb-3">
                            üí∞ The $1,475 Fee
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">
                            You must pay this by credit card upon submission. It
                            is <strong>non-refundable</strong> even if your application
                            is rejected immediately.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="bg-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-indigo-100"
                    >
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-indigo-900 text-lg mb-3">
                            üìÑ Document Upload Rules
                        </h3>
                        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-indigo-800">
                            <li class="flex items-center">
                                <span class="mr-2">üìÑ</span>
                                <strong>Format:</strong> PDF only.
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center">
                                <span class="mr-2">‚öñÔ∏è</span>
                                <strong>Size Limit:</strong> 3MB per file.
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center">
                                <span class="mr-2">üì∑</span>
                                <strong>Quality:</strong> Color scans. No phone pics.
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center">
                                <span class="mr-2">üè∑Ô∏è</span>
                                <strong>Naming:</strong>
                                <code>Passport_Bio_Name.pdf</code>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="my-8">
                    <h3>The "Job Offer Form"</h3>
                    <p>
                        Your employer must sign a specific 8-10 page PDF form.
                        This is where most errors happen.
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 p-6 rounded-r-xl my-4 not-prose"
                    >
                        <p
                            class="font-bold text-red-800 mb-1 text-sm uppercase tracking-wide"
                        >
                            Employer Warning
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-red-900 text-sm font-medium">
                            Many employers are lazy about this form. You need to
                            sit with them and ensure they fill it out correctly.
                            If they check "No" on "Business License Valid?",
                            your application dies instantly.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <hr class="my-12 border-slate-200" />

                <h2>Phase 3: The Waiting Game (Processing)</h2>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 not-prose my-6">
                    <div class="bg-slate-100 p-4 rounded-xl text-center">
                        <span
                            class="block text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-1"
                            >~3 Months</span
                        >
                        <span
                            class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-wide"
                            >Standard Processing</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-blue-100 p-4 rounded-xl text-center">
                        <span
                            class="block text-3xl font-black text-blue-900 mb-1"
                            >2-4 Weeks</span
                        >
                        <span
                            class="text-sm text-blue-800 font-bold uppercase tracking-wide"
                            >Tech Stream</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-amber-100 p-4 rounded-xl text-center">
                        <span
                            class="block text-3xl font-black text-amber-900 mb-1"
                            >Anytime</span
                        >
                        <span
                            class="text-sm text-amber-800 font-bold uppercase tracking-wide"
                            >Verification Call</span
                        >
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-6">
                    <strong>Note:</strong> An officer *will* call your employer. Warn
                    your boss. If they miss the call or sound confused about who you
                    are, it triggers a Procedural Fairness Letter.
                </p>

                <div
                    class="bg-slate-900 text-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl not-prose"
                >
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2 flex items-center">
                        <span
                            class="bg-red-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mr-3 uppercase"
                            >Danger</span
                        >
                        Procedural Fairness Letter (PFL)
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm mb-4">
                        This is a terrifying letter saying <em
                            >"We intend to refuse your application because X.
                            You have 7 days to respond."</em
                        >
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 border-t border-slate-700 pt-4"
                    >
                        <div>
                            <span
                                class="block text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1"
                                >Trigger 1</span
                            >
                            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-white"
                                >Wage on paystubs != Job Offer</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span
                                class="block text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1"
                                >Trigger 2</span
                            >
                            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-white"
                                >Duties don't match NOC</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span
                                class="block text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1"
                                >Trigger 3</span
                            >
                            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-white"
                                >Missing Business License</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <hr class="my-12 border-slate-200" />

                <h2>Phase 4: Nomination & Federal Application</h2>
                <p>
                    If approved, you get a "Nomination Certificate" via email.
                </p>

                <h3>Work Permit Support Letter</h3>
                <p>
                    Along with the certificate, you get a "Work Permit Support
                    Letter" (WPSL). Use this to renew your work permit
                    immediately if yours is expiring.
                </p>

                <h3>Applying for PR</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Express Entry:</strong> Update your EE profile with
                        the Nomination Certificate data. You will get +600 points
                        within 24 hours. Wait for next draw -> ITA -> Apply.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Non-Express Entry:</strong> Submit a PR application
                        through the <a href="https://www.canada.ca/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/account.html" class="text-blue-600 underline" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"
                            >IRCC Permanent Residence Portal</a
                        > (New online system).
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <hr class="my-12 border-slate-200" />

                <h2 id="faq">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                <div class="space-y-4 not-prose my-8">
                    <details
                        class="group bg-slate-50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 open:bg-white open:ring-1 open:ring-blue-100 open:shadow-md transition-all"
                    >
                        <summary
                            class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center outline-none"
                        >
                            <span
