                                >‚ñº</span
                            >
                        </summary>
                        <div
                            class="mt-4 text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100 pt-4 animate-fadeIn"
                        >
                            Yes, you can update details like "Current Wage" or
                            "Language Score" in your SIRS profile <strong
                                >as long as you haven't been invited yet</strong
                            >. Once invited, the profile locks.
                        </div>
                    </details>

                    <details
                        class="group bg-slate-50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 open:bg-white open:ring-1 open:ring-blue-100 open:shadow-md transition-all"
                    >
                        <summary
                            class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center outline-none"
                        >
                            <span
                                >What happens if I quit my job after applying?</span
                            >
                            <span
                                class="transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180 text-blue-500"
                                >‚ñº</span
                            >
                        </summary>
                        <div
                            class="mt-4 text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100 pt-4 animate-fadeIn"
                        >
                            You must inform BC PNP immediately. Your application
                            will usually be put on "Hold" until you find a new
                            job that also qualifies. If you don't find one, your
                            application is refused.
                        </div>
                    </details>

                    <details
                        class="group bg-slate-50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 open:bg-white open:ring-1 open:ring-blue-100 open:shadow-md transition-all"
                    >
                        <summary
                            class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center outline-none"
                        >
                            <span>Does BC PNP interview me?</span>
                            <span
                                class="transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180 text-blue-500"
                                >‚ñº</span
                            >
                        </summary>
                        <div
                            class="mt-4 text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100 pt-4 animate-fadeIn"
                        >
                            Rarely in person. They usually interview your
                            employer by phone. They typically only interview you
                            if they suspect immigration fraud or if your job
                            duties are unclear.
                        </div>
                    </details>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="bg-blue-900 text-white p-8 rounded-2xl text-center mt-12"
                >
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Ready to Start?</h2>
                    <p class="text-blue-200 mb-6">
                        First step: Check your score. If it's too low, don't
                        register yet‚Äîimprove your profile first.
                    </p>
                    <a
                        href="/bc-pnp-calculator"
                        class="inline-block bg-white text-blue-900 font-bold px-8 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors"
                    >
                        Calculate Points ‚Üí
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Related Guides -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Related Guides</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-3">
                    <li>
                        <a
                            href="/articles/bc-pnp-documents-checklist"
                            class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium"
                        >
                            BC PNP Document Checklist 2026 ‚Üí
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a
                            href="/articles/bc-pnp-processing-times"
                            class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium"
                        >
                            BC PNP Processing Times 2026 ‚Üí
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a
                            href="/articles/bc-pnp-cost-guide-2026"
                            class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium"
                        >
                            BC PNP Cost Guide: Complete Budget Breakdown ‚Üí
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a
                            href="/articles/bc-pnp-common-mistakes"
                            class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium"
                        >
                            15 Common BC PNP Mistakes to Avoid ‚Üí
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a
                            href="/articles/bc-pnp-after-nomination"
                            class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium"
                        >
                            After BC PNP Nomination: Next Steps ‚Üí
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>
</BaseLayout>
